name: Kashyyyk: Sacred Forest
LocationDStext: Unless Mosep on table, Force lost from your Force drains here must come from opponent's hand, if possible.  All Nudjs are lost.  (Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)
LocationLStext: At start of your turn, may draw a card from Reserve Deck for each Kashyyyk site where all your ability is provided by Wookiees. Once per turn, may deploy Yarna d'al' Gargan from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
